/*
---
title: Font Sizes
description: |
    Font sizes are fuzzified by names. Available sizes are:

    - small
    - normal
    - accent
    - large
    - big
    - epic
---
*/

for set in (small 14 24) (normal 16 24) (accent 18 24) (large 20 24) (big 24 36) (epic 32 36)
    $font-size-{set[0]}
        font-size unit(set[1], "px")
        line-height unit(set[2], "px")
